text: Parametaria is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails. ==Species== Species within the genus Parametaria include:Biolib Encyclopedia of life * Parametaria dupontii Kiener, 1845 * Parametaria epamella P.
